            <h2>PREMIVAL Platform</h2>
            <p
              class="list"
            >Premival.com (hereinafter called the "PREMIVAL Platform") is committed to safeguarding your privacy online. Please read the following policy to understand how your personal information will be treated as you make full use of the PREMIVAL platform.</p>
