            <p>Our sites may contain links to other Web sites over which we have no control. DESOL COMPANY LIMITED, which owns and operates PREMIVAL Website and App, is not responsible for the privacy policies or practices of other Websites to which you choose to link from a PREMIVAL website. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of those other websites so you can understand how they collect, use and share your information. This Privacy Policy applies solely to the information we collect on a PREMIVAL website, and does not apply to information we collect in any other fashion.</p>
            <h2>This policy will let you know:</h2>
