            <p>Advertising networks that serve jobs onto the PREMIVAL.com career website may also use their own cookies. PREMIVAL will also gather or may gather certain information about your use of our site, such as what areas you visit and what services you access. Moreover, there is information about your computer hardware and software that is or may be collected by PREMIVAL. This information can include without limitation your IP address, browser type, domain names, access items and referring website addresses.</p>
            <h3>How your information is used?</h3>
            <p>By submitting your information, You agree that PREMIVAL, its affiliates, subsidiaries and other related entities under DESOL Company may use your information we gather whether personal, demographic, collective or technical, for the purpose of operating and improving the PREMIVAL website, fostering a positive user experience or introducing and delivering the products and services that we or they offer.</p>
            <p>We may use your contact information in order to send you e-mail or other communications regarding updates at the PREMIVAL website and our Services and Products. The nature and frequency of these messages will vary depending upon the information we have about you. In addition, at the time of registration, you have the option to elect to receive additional communications, information and promotions including without limitation free informational newsletters from PREMIVAL relating to topics that may be of special interest to you.</p>
            <p>We have an area where you can contact us. Any feedback you send to us becomes our property, and we can use such feedback (such as success stories) for marketing purposes or contact you for further information.</p>
            <h3>Who is collecting your information?</h3>
            <p>When you are asked for personal information on the PREMIVAL Website, you are sharing that information with the PREMIVAL Website alone, unless it is specifically stated otherwise. However, some activities will, by their very nature, result in your personal information being revealed to other users of the PREMIVAL Website. For example, when you enter personal information on the job posting form, this information will generally be included in your job, unless specifically stated otherwise</p>
